div.div:
The MotionEvent#location attribute MUST be composed of two additional GeoJSON's properties which are:
- The building (related to the FeatureOfInterest#feature) from which this MotionEvent occurred. This property MUST be named "building" an use an integer typed value
- The building's floor from which this MotionEvent occurred. This property MUST be named "floor" and use an integer typed value
